143
00:09:09.340 --> 00:09:10.540
If she's dead.

144
00:09:10.620 --> 00:09:12.980
maybe you can use this
to tell me how she died.

145
00:09:14.740 --> 00:09:15.860
I can give it a go.

146
00:09:26.100 --> 00:09:28.540
Yeah. definitely
a feminine energy.

147
00:09:29.580 --> 00:09:31.100
