153
00:09:58.020 --> 00:09:59.996
Was she strangled?

154
00:10:00.020 --> 00:10:00.100
Was she strangled?

155
00:10:00.300 --> 00:10:02.340
Are you telling me
someone strangled her?

156
00:10:04.340 --> 00:10:05.820
