157
00:10:05.900 --> 00:10:08.700
- Tell me how Claire Harris died.
- I can't!

158
00:10:08.780 --> 00:10:10.420
- Tell me how she died.
- I can't!

159
00:10:10.500 --> 00:10:11.620
Damien!

160
