sat and I can't get through.

269
00:20:24.100 --> 00:20:26.580
Anyway. how alarmed
should we be?

270
00:20:26.660 --> 00:20:27.900
Well. she's not stupid.

271
00:20:27.980 --> 00:20:30.740
