305
00:22:39.220 --> 00:22:40.676
You've reached
Sergeant Andie Whitford

306
00:22:40.700 --> 00:22:43.780
of Brokenridge Police.
Leave a detailed message.

307
00:22:56.820 --> 00:22:58.236
Mind if I sit this
