308
00:22:58.260 --> 00:22:59.540
Of course.

309
00:22:59.620 --> 00:22:59.997
Damien's gone to batten down
the hatches at the shop.

310
00:23:00.021 --> 00:23:02.340
Damien's gone to batten down
the hatches at the shop.

311
