fucking brumbies.

326
00:24:18.140 --> 00:24:19.860
Whoa!

327
00:24:32.540 --> 00:24:34.060
Oh fuck it!

328
00:25:02.380 --> 00:25:05.540
Hey. hey. hey. hey. hey.
