333
00:25:21.940 --> 00:25:24.500
Come on! Hit me!

334
00:25:24.580 --> 00:25:26.940
Yeah!

335
00:25:27.020 --> 00:25:28.900
Archie!

336
00:25:28.980 --> 00:25:31.180
Archie!

337
00:25:46.180 --> 00:25:48.300
