374
00:27:51.660 --> 00:27:55.300
Hey. I am glad
you moved up here.

375
00:27:56.180 --> 00:27:58.220
You're kind of strange.

376
00:27:59.460 --> 00:27:59.997
but I like that.

377
00:28:00.021 --> 00:28:01.100
but I like that.

378
