403
00:29:43.220 --> 00:29:45.140
I've seen things
that I can't explain.

404
00:29:45.620 --> 00:29:47.740
and things that I
shouldn't have seen.

405
00:29:48.740 --> 00:29:49.580
I mean. a lot of people think

406
00:29:49.620 --> 00:29:51.220
