445
00:32:21.180 --> 00:32:23.420
I shouldn't have brought
you up here. mate.

446
00:32:24.380 --> 00:32:26.060
I'm so sorry.

447
00:32:30.780 --> 00:32:32.700
I'm so sorry.

448
00:32:37.540 --> 00:32:39.420
