reported it stolen.

458
00:33:32.900 --> 00:33:35.140
- Copy that.
- Thanks.

459
00:33:38.420 --> 00:33:41.300
Thanks again. for last night.

460
00:33:41.380 --> 00:33:43.060
Well. thank that old man.

461
00:33:43.140 --> 00:33:44.860
He's the one who
sent me out of here.

462
