- Owen.

463
00:33:50.620 --> 00:33:51.956
What the hell were you thinking?

464
00:33:51.980 --> 00:33:53.220
Coming up here on your own.

465
00:33:53.300 --> 00:33:54.980
I was following a lead.

466
00:33:55.060 --> 00:33:56.740
